.None\n            repairNamespaces = true\n        }\n        val serializer = String.serializer()\n        val rootName = QName(ROOT_NAMESPACE, \"message\", \"msg\")\n        val value = \"Hello <native> & XML\"\n\n        val encoded: String = xml.encodeToString(serializer, value, rootName)\n\n        assertThat(encoded)\n            .contains(\"<msg:message\")\n            .contains(\"xmlns:msg=\\\"$ROOT_NAMESPACE\\\"\")\n            .contains(\"Hello &lt;native&gt; &amp; XML\")\n            .contains(\"</msg:message>\")\n        assertThat(xml.decodeFromString(serializer, encoded, rootName)).isEqualTo(value)\n    }\n\n    @Test\n    fun configuredXmlDeclarationAndGenericParserRoundTripCollectionRoot(): Unit {\n        val xml = XML {\n            xmlDeclMode = XmlDeclMode.Minimal\n            defaultToGenericParser = true\n            indentString = \"  \"\n        }\n        val serializer = ListSerializer(String.serializer())\n        val rootName = QName(\"\", \"aliases\")\n        val values = listOf(\"graal\", \"native-image\", \"xmlutil\")\n\n        val encoded: String = xml.encodeToString(serializer, values, rootName)\n\n        assertThat(encoded).startsWith(\"<?xml version=\")\n        assertThat(encoded)\n            .contains(\"<aliases>\")\n            .contains(\"graal\")\n            .contains(\"native-image\")\n            .contains(\"xmlutil\")\n        assertThat(xml.decodeFromString(serializer, encoded, rootName)).isEqualTo(values)\n    }\n\n    private companion object {\n        private const val ROOT_NAMESPACE: String = \"urn:test:explicit-root\"\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1804, "output": 1269, "cacheRead": 95232, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 98305, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777906053779, "responseId": "resp_0066cfd37b3aaa770169f8b186b12c81939171f002c8fd9bda"}}
